<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TrapRoyalties – Unclaimed Royalty Recovery</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html, body { height: 100%; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 10%, #0b1f4e 0%, #020b22 45%, #020818 100%);
            color: #e7ecff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            padding: 14px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(94,109,255,0.15);
        }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .logo-icon { background: #5e6dff; width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(94,109,255,0.4); }
        .logo-text { font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; }
        .logo-text span { color: #5e6dff; font-weight: 400; }
        .nav-btn { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

        /* Hero — takes up remaining screen */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(94,109,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(94,109,255,0.3);
            padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
            color: #a8b5d9; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .badge-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: #5e6dff; border-radius: 50%; animation: ping 1.4s infinite; }
        @keyframes ping { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scale(1.3)} }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(36px, 9vw, 64px);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #e7ecff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(94,109,255,0.3);
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(14px, 3.5vw, 18px);
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 400;
            max-width: 480px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .btn-unlock {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #5e6dff, #7c65ff);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(94,109,255,0.35);
            transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 360px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn-unlock:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(94,109,255,0.45); }

        .btn-sub {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #475569;
            letter-spacing: 0.18em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #334155;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="logo">
        <div class="logo-icon">R</div>
        <div class="logo-text">TrapRoyalties <span>[Audit Division]</span></div>
    </div>
    <a href="/lawyer/doja_cat_nicki_minaj_agora_hills_remix" class="nav-btn">RECOVERY PORTAL</a>
</header>

<main>
    <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        2026 Statutory Audit Active
    </div>

    <h1>Get Your Bag<br>From Every Stream,<br>Sync &amp; Performance</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
        Our specialized systems audit 2024–2025 registries to find the unallocated black box revenue major labels missed. Get your money back.
    </p>

    <a href="/lawyer/doja_cat_nicki_minaj_agora_hills_remix" class="btn-unlock">
        Unlock Full Audit Report
    </a>
    <p class="btn-sub">One-time fee of $150 &nbsp;·&nbsp; No royalty percentage taken &nbsp;·&nbsp; Most artists recover 10x–50x their investment</p>
</main>

<footer>
    TrapRoyalties &nbsp;·&nbsp; Statutory Asset Recovery Bureau &nbsp;·&nbsp; 2026 Audit &nbsp;·&nbsp; Not affiliated with SoundExchange
</footer>

</body>
</html>
